<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-16"?> <Root LookupSqlQuery="SELECT DISTINCT l.satsang_centre_id, d.centre_cd, d.centre_nm FROM generic_sewadar_lists l
JOIN satsang_centres_details d ON d.satsang_centre_id = l.satsang_centre_id
